# SERVICE

## address

### DESCRIPTION

Address service for postal address support.
Provides help-visible metadata for CNCF projections.

### OPERATION

#### lookupAddress

##### DESCRIPTION

Look up an address by postal code.
Returns a normalized address representation.

##### IN

| 名前         | 型     | 多重度 | 説明        |
|--------------+--------+--------+-------------|
| postalCode   | string | 1      | postal code |

##### OUT

| 名前    | 型     | 多重度 | 説明   |
|---------+--------+--------+--------|
| address | string | 1      | result |

# ENTITY

## Person

### ATTRIBUTE

| name | type     | multiplicity |
|------+----------+--------------|
| id   | entityid | 1            |
| name | name     | 1            |
